            else (Word8Array.update arr i nl;
                  SOME (Word8Array.substring arr 0 (i+1)))
        else inputLine_aux (extend_array arr) i
      in inputLine_aux (Word8Array.array 127 (Word8.fromInt 0)) 0 end`;

